{"title":"CLAUDE.md 实践总结","uid":"d11a07364b7f3779a6408f2f168b8c7e","slug":"claude","date":"2026-04-09T03:10:37.595Z","updated":"2026-04-14T02:32:12.755Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/claude.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://telegraph-image-new.vercel.app/api/cfile/AgACAgUAAyEGAASHUuUOAAOBadccY9kHqsr6jjpbeEjpn55OezwAAhIOaxsHgrlWZNeXcbKEjzoBAAMCAAN5AAM7BA","content":"<p>本文总结介绍如何通过定义claude.md以及rules来提高claude code的开发效率，让claude code生成的代码更符合项目规范和个人习惯。</p>\n<h3 id=\"CLAUDE-md-做什么的？\"><a href=\"http://CLAUDE.md\">CLAUDE.md</a> 做什么的？</h3>\n<p>简单来说是编写指令给claude code提供持久上下文。</p>\n<h3 id=\"CLAUDE-md-定义在哪里？\"><a href=\"http://CLAUDE.md\">CLAUDE.md</a> 定义在哪里？</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>组织目录：/Library/Application Support/ClaudeCode/CLAUDE.md</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>用户目录：~/.claude/CLAUDE.md</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>项目目录：./CLAUDE.md 或者 ./.claude/CLAUDE.md 或者 <a href=\"http://CLAUDE.local.md\">CLAUDE.local.md</a></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>注意 <a href=\"http://CLAUDE.local.md\">CLAUDE.local.md</a> 会被应用但不应该被提交</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>子文件目录：./src/CLAUDE.md</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>子目录内的 <code>CLAUDE.md</code> 文件不会全部加载，只有当claude code从这些目录中实际读取内容时才会加载</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>当有多个文件时，按照最后加载的优先级更高：更接近的目录 &gt; 项目 &gt; 用户</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\"># 系统中的目录示例</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">└──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> /</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">    └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> .claude</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">        └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> CLAUDE.md</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">    └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> Library</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">        └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> Application</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> Support</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">            └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> ClaudeCode</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">                └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> CLAUDE.md</span></span></code></pre>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\"># 项目中的目录示例</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">├──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> .claude</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">│</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">   ├──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> rules</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">│</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">   └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> CLAUDE.md</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">├──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> src</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">│</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">   ├──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> app</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">│</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">   └──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> CLAUDE.md</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">├──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> CLAUDE.md</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B392F0\">└──</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> README.md</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"如何创建CLAUDE-md\"><a href=\"http://xn--CLAUDE-hl9ik3qimtc2m.md\">如何创建CLAUDE.md</a>?</h3>\n<p>启动claude code，然后输入 <code>/init</code>。<a href=\"http://xn--CLAUDE-9m7iglm8ez6lypat22jvkbs9ao49a57rkss3x3bmwb835v73qb.md\">这会根据当前项目创建一个广泛的CLAUDE.md</a>。但是一般需要二次更改，因为这个生成的并不一定能有效的规范claude code生成代码。而且CLAUDE.md会占用上下文，所以这个文件也并不是越大越好。</p>\n<h3 id=\"如何更改CLAUDE-md\"><a href=\"http://xn--CLAUDE-hl9it80eh9xt1d.md\">如何更改CLAUDE.md</a>?</h3>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>添加最有用的信息！！！</p>\n<p>要具体指出规则而不是含糊描述！！！</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>方法不超过50行✅</p>\n<p>方法尽量精简❌</p></blockquote>\n<p>如果不能帮助claude code减少错误则没必要写入！！！</p>\n<p>每个 <a href=\"http://CLAUDE.md\">CLAUDE.md</a> 文件目标在 200 行以下！！！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>常用命令：构建，测试，lint，本地开发</li>\n<li>项目特有的限制或者依赖</li>\n<li>工作流程：分支命名，提交代码前检测，提交信息规则</li>\n<li>文件职责：不同目录下的功能职责以及限制</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"如何拆分CLAUDE-md\"><a href=\"http://xn--CLAUDE-hl9iw7pwrt00v.md\">如何拆分CLAUDE.md</a>?</h3>\n<p>当项目越来越大规则越来越多，可以使用<code>@path/to/import</code>来拆分CLAUDE.md将详细的规则限制放入不同文件中。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\"># 项目根目录 CLAUDE.md</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">See @README.md for project overview.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">See @package.json for available commands and scripts.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">See @docs/testing.md for testing conventions.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">See @docs/api-guidelines.md for API design rules.</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"持续更新\">持续更新</h3>\n<p>当多次发现claude code犯同样的错误时，这就是一个强烈的预警你需要更新你的CLAUDE.md了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"Claude-code-通知提醒\">Claude code 通知提醒</h3>\n<p>当开多个claude code时候，任务完成后claude code没有任何通知，我们需要定时查看是否任务完成，但是它有hooks可以在不同的阶段来执行一些脚本，我们可以用它来做一个系统通知。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color:#24292e;color:#e1e4e8\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">\"hooks\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\">    // Claude 完成回复/停止时发送一个系统通知</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    \"Stop\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">      &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">        \"hooks\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">          &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">            \"type\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: </span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">\"command\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">            \"command\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: </span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">\"/Users/kidwen/.claude/complete-notification.sh\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">          &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">        ]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">      &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">    ],</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#6A737D\">    //  Claude Code 需要你注意时（比如等你回答问题、需要权限确认等）发送通知</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">    \"Notification\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">      &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">        \"matcher\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: </span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">\"\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">        \"hooks\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: [</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">          &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">            \"type\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: </span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">\"command\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">            \"command\"</span><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">: </span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">\"osascript -e 'display notification </span><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">\\\"</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">Claude Code needs your attention</span><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">\\\"</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\"> with title </span><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">\\\"</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">Claude Code</span><span style=\"color:#79B8FF\">\\\"</span><span style=\"color:#9ECBFF\">'\"</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">          &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">        ]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">      &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">    ],</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#E1E4E8\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre>\n<